Name: Leaf Tornado
Desc:
Jumps and spins while shooting arrows in all four directions. This skill can only be used only in midair with a certain height or above. Requires a higher height when chaining with Gust Dive. Can be chained with Gust Dive, Rolling Moonsault, Spikes Royale, and Wrath of Enreal.
Lv. 10 Effect: Can learn the 4th Job Skill, Spikes Royale
